---
// Asymmetric hero: copy anchored left, the ouroboros mark living large and faint
// on the right, rotating slowly — the eternal-loop motif behind the name. Load
// reveals are staggered via --reveal-delay so the page assembles top-to-bottom.
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-line">
  <div class="bg-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-24 top-1/2 hidden -translate-y-1/2 lg:block"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <span
      class="ouroboros-spin block size-[34rem] bg-accent/[0.06]"
      style="mask:url(/ouroboros.svg) center/contain no-repeat;-webkit-mask:url(/ouroboros.svg) center/contain no-repeat"
    ></span>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-28 sm:px-8 sm:py-36 lg:py-44">
    <p class="reveal eyebrow" style="--reveal-delay:0ms">
      Ourovoros — Developers Collective
    </p>

    <h1
      class="reveal mt-6 max-w-3xl font-display text-5xl font-semibold leading-[1.04] tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"
      style="--reveal-delay:80ms"
    >
      Two senior engineers for
      <span class="text-accent">systems design</span> and
      <span class="text-accent">low-level efficiency</span>.
    </h1>

    <p
      class="reveal mt-7 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted"
      style="--reveal-delay:160ms"
    >
      We take novel ideas and turn them into correct, efficient systems — and
      the developer tooling around them.
    </p>

    <div
      class="reveal mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-4"
      style="--reveal-delay:240ms"
    >
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-sm bg-accent px-5 py-3 font-mono text-sm tracking-wider text-bg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        START A PROJECT
        <span class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#tooling"
        class="font-mono text-sm tracking-wider text-muted underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:text-ink hover:underline"
        >View our open-source tooling</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ouroboros-spin {
    animation: ouroboros-rotate 90s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes ouroboros-rotate {
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }
</style>
